org.apache.iceberg.metrics

Interface MetricsReporter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LoggingMetricsReporter
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface MetricsReporter
    This interface defines the basic API for reporting metrics for operations to a Table.

      • report

        void report(MetricsReport report)
        Indicates that a operation is done by reporting a MetricsReport. A MetricsReport is usually directly derived from a MetricsReport instance.
        Parameters:
        report - The MetricsReport to report.
